#: ../../hardware/controllers/mixvibes_u_mix_control_2.md:1
msgid "MixVibes U-Mix Control (Pro) 2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/mixvibes_u_mix_control_2.md:4
msgid ""
"The MixVibes U-Mix Control Pro 2 is a MIDI DJ controller with an **internal "
"soundcard** and **two Inputs** for Turntables or any Audio-Source with RCA. "
"It offers also a **changeable** Cross-fader, **adjustable** Cross-Fader "
"**Curve** and **individual Touch-Level-Sensors**. The U-Mix Control **Pro** "
"differs only in Cue-Button-Labels The U-Mix Control 2 (without “Pro” = "
"internal soundcard) also. Both should work fine with this MIDI mapping."
msgstr ""

